#!/usr/bin/env bash

#### crowsnest - A webcam Service for multiple Cams and Stream Services.
####
#### Written by Stephan Wendel aka KwadFan <me@stephanwe.de>
#### Copyright 2021
#### https://github.com/mainsail-crew/crowsnest
